bilingual.source: The credit rating agency decided to downgrade the country's rating.
bilingual.target: 信用评级机构决定降级该国的评级。
他们的信用评级被降级了。

bilingual.source: The credit rating of the issuer is very important to investors.
bilingual.target: 发行人的信用评级对投资者非常重要。

bilingual.source: The credit rating of the company was downgraded by the financial agency.
bilingual.target: 该公司的信用评级被金融机构降级了。

bilingual.source: The explicitness of the movie's content required a higher age rating.
bilingual.target: 电影内容的明确性要求更高的年龄评级。

bilingual.source: Often the star rating I give has far more to do with the kind of day I'm having.
bilingual.target: 通常，我给的星级评级与我今天过得怎么样有很大关系。

bilingual.source: BBB- is the lowest investment grade rating.
Could face a downgrade of its credit rating
Its bond rating is barely above junk.
bilingual.target: 其债券评级是略高于垃圾。

yingyinNormal.en: The rating agencies, the banks, the fucking government, you're saying they're all asleep at the wheel?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是说评级机构，银行和狗屁政府都坐视不管吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And when the pile gets large enough, the whole thing is suddenly considered diversified and the whores at the rating agency give it a 92%-93% AAA rating, no questions asked.
yingyinNormal.zh: 堆得足够多了看起来就极具多样性了，评级机构的混蛋们就把它评为含有92%到93%AAA级资产的债券，没有人怀疑。

yingyinNormal.en: A while back, YouTube changed its user interface from a star-based rating system to a thumbs-up rating system.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不久前，YouTube把它用户界面的评分系统从打星改成了点赞。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
